Sample Entry: Discrete values for every row entry: LI, LZ
Label: Location Inventory ID
Description: Record identifier for location inventory. 'LI' for Location Inventory, 'LZ' for Location Zero/Special status.

Sample Entry: Applicable for every row. 592 unique values. Samples: AELZ37, GBAPPTUL011, GOT1000416, CGRVA115301, GCA08P, CISB81007,  CIRWA1000DF
Label: Product Code
Description: Product code or item number stored at this location. 592 unique products tracked.

Sample Entry: Text/Mixed data. 16 unique values. Samples: S5, S5, P1, PS, P1, B3, BR, D2, MG, ML, MM, MW, MZ, P1, PP, PS, S4
Label: Warehouse
Description: Warehouse code where inventory is located. 16 warehouses (S5, P1, PS, B3, BR, D2, MG, ML, MM, MW, MZ, PP, S4).

Sample Entry: Constant value of '          ' for all entries, not being used.
Label: Lot Number
Description: Lot or batch number for inventory tracking. Currently not in use (blank).

Sample Entry: Mixed data, not applicable to every row entry.. 196 unique values. Samples: Numericals from 140 to 1000: e.g., 250, 272, 394, 415, 541, , then from 10000 e.g., 10054, 10063, Mixed values such as: LS5   , MZ    , PS    , 858, MZ
Label: Location Code
Description: Specific location or bin within the warehouse. 196 different locations, mix of numeric (140-10063) and alphanumeric codes.

Sample Entry: Lots of 0's (94.7%), Range from -0.931 to 0.999, Contains decimal values
Label: Opening Balance
Description: Opening inventory balance for the lot/location. Mostly zero with small decimal adjustments.

Sample Entry: Constant value of '0.0' for all entries
Label: Issues Quantity
Description: Total quantity issued from this location inventory.

Label: Adjustments
Description: Inventory adjustments made. Small values indicating minor corrections.

Label: Receipts Quantity
Description: Total quantity received into this location inventory.

Sample Entry: Constant value of '0.0' for all entries
Label: Allocated Quantity
Description: Quantity currently allocated or reserved for orders.

Sample Entry: Constant value of '20091231.0' for all entries
